SCOPE & PROVENANCE (important)
------------------------------
This repository is a community **port** of NetPay's official Magento module and it
**bundles NetPay's PHP SDK** (the `Sdk/` directory). Those underlying components are
the property of **NetPay** and are covered by NetPay's own (proprietary) terms.

The license granted here is given by the port author over the **port contributions**
in this repository (the adaptation to Magento 2.4.8 / PHP 8.4, the fixes, the
multi-store and 3-D Secure work, documentation, etc.). It does **not** grant any
rights to NetPay's underlying software or SDK. Your use of the NetPay components is
also subject to NetPay's terms; obtain the appropriate authorization from NetPay for
your use case.

